item.title: Hierarchical Data Format (HDF5) v2.13.1.143
item.description:
Product: Hierarchical Data Format (HDF5) v2.13.1.143
Company: Martijn Jasperse
Release Date: Mon, 24 Feb 2020 10:24:18 -0500
Packager: Martijn Jasperse

Description: This library provides a simple interface to read and write data stored in the Heirarchical Data Format (HDF), version 5. This is a multi-lingual cross-platform format permitting storage of data with descriptive meta-data in an object hierarchy within a single file. See http://www.hdfgroup.org/why_hdf/ for more information.

Release Notes: <b>Now supports <u>timestamps and analog waveforms</u></b>

Requires <b>HDF5 v1.8.14</b>. You may need to uninstall earlier versions if the installer fails, see the FAQ for more details.

See <i>CHANGES.TXT</i> for a description of changes since the last version.
item.dc:creator: Martijn Jasperse
